00Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dd1aca9856c28360af901031b802bc32522f1628","tid":1711050,"uid":95872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"Quick"},{"pid":"fb56b1f5d830a67c7361f87f73874536eb6bcecc","tid":1711050,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:41:48.000Z","msg":"又想撞山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54128fd8bff13d8573cafa77c3168f9c0609338","tid":1711050,"uid":30723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:42:30.000Z","msg":"頂係咪舊文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日聽"},{"pid":"0daaf595bcd97dcf31278998b6acb2f70f6f84dc","tid":1711050,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80cca02f8489242c2e2ef064aa48a6491543299c","tid":1711050,"uid":136467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"月圓之夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中秋夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6dfdc57d48c10ee2a5f181dc97f7c13ec61bda42","tid":1711050,"uid":1285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"每個禮拜copy &amp; paste篇文一次?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1e832a7d1765426d2998de4d690dc74275f187","tid":1711050,"uid":150347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"模擬突擊香港　解放軍墜機11死<br />\n<br />\n解放軍第75集團軍本月初在湖南模擬突擊香港演習，其間一架最新型的直-8G直升機墜毀。據中國人權民運信息中心昨消息指，事故導致11名解放軍死亡，其中三人為駕駛軍官，本月初才參加了十．一天安門閱兵。據信息中心統計，解放軍今年以來已至少發生三宗同類意外。中共昨未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n信息中心報道，南部戰區第75集團軍「第121空中突擊旅」於本月11日進行「突擊香港」演練，被模擬為香港的是湖南漵浦縣。當日，這架直-8G直升機從廣西崇左市出發，突擊800公里外漵浦縣，結果在當晚7時許撞山墜毀，機上三名駕駛軍官及八名士兵全部死亡。<br />\n至少3宗同類意外<br />\n機上最高軍階的為溫姓中校，與機上另外兩名軍官曾參加今年十．一天安門閱兵。解放軍只有兩個空中突擊旅，一個為今次出事的「第121空中突擊旅」，兩個基地分別距港690公里及720公里；另一個為中部戰區83集團軍的空中突擊第161旅。<br />\n<br />\n121旅使用的直-8G是大型運輸直升機，本月12日才於天津直升機展覽首度亮相。據軍方介紹，直-8G可搭載30名全副武裝人員飛行1,000公里，重13噸，是目前國產最大直升機。<br />\n<br />\n信息中心統計，解放軍今年至少發生三宗直升機墜毀意外。今年4月26日，一架直-10直升機於河北保定閱兵訓練時墜毀；今年5月13日，一架米-17直升機在秦嶺地區墜毀，六名解放軍死亡。<br />\n中國人權民運信息中心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20191031/F54PUX74LTJWAQ4YDIEPLXIQ2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191031%2FF54PUX74LTJWAQ4YDIEPLXIQ2E%2F&d=9CaroZtPfqcCLVRp0XVEkQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=868480db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191031%2FF54PUX74LTJWAQ4YDIEPLXIQ2E%2F&h=3e70b0ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20191031/F54PUX74LTJWAQ4YDIEPLXIQ2E/</a>"},{"pid":"8edb219b0bd5610c5d23bca87b327226ffa28387","tid":1711050,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"武警在港 共軍在港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd9aa0b33e356f4e1991a0b6fbe6aa9b075ed01","tid":1711050,"uid":231711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"又拉一派 打一派"},{"pid":"eeea7549296ebb322348f34715383c580802f413","tid":1711050,"uid":262435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"佢老母個臭閪近公廁"},{"pid":"441c89845660cb904da65bfa5008e8a6add9fcee","tid":1711050,"uid":148980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:00:43.000Z","msg":"進進日日打飛機但係射唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27d7863c47174bd051e329d7029895c62a39729","tid":1711050,"uid":22069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"出左Call我<br />\n習曱甴"},{"pid":"91e4d8cc58a82c447084360e6b15a8ea6e396ef0","tid":1711050,"uid":38535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"